<h2 id="introduction">1. Introduction:</h2>
<p>The Advanced AI Chatbot Framework developed by 10Pearls Organization is a cutting-edge solution designed to revolutionize customer interaction through intelligent conversational interfaces. This framework leverages state-of-the-art natural language processing (NLP) algorithms and machine learning techniques to create chatbots capable of understanding and responding to user queries in real-time.</p>
<h2 id="system-requirements">2. System Requirements:</h2>
<h3 id="hardware-requirements">Hardware Requirements:</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Processor: Intel Core i7 or equivalent</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>RAM: 8GB or higher</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Storage: 50GB free disk space</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Display: 1280x800 resolution or higher</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Internet Connection: Broadband connection</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="software-requirements">Software Requirements:</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Operating System: Windows 10 or macOS 10.14+</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Web Browser: Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Safari</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Additional Software: Python 3.7+, Node.js, Docker</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="installation">3. Installation:</h2>
<ol>
<li>
<p>Download the Advanced AI Chatbot Framework package from the official 10Pearls website.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Install Python and Node.js if not already installed on your system.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Navigate to the directory containing the downloaded package.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Run the installation script and follow the on-screen instructions.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Configure the necessary settings during installation, including API keys and authentication tokens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Complete the installation process and verify successful installation by launching the chatbot interface.</p>
</li>
</ol>
