<h2 id="troubleshooting">6. Troubleshooting:</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Issue</strong>: Chatbot fails to recognize user intents accurately.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Re-train the chatbot model with additional training data and optimize the NLP algorithms.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Issue</strong>: Chatbot responses are delayed.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Solution</strong>: Check the system resources and optimize performance by scaling up hardware resources if necessary.</p>
<h2 id="faqs">7. FAQs:</h2>
<p><strong>Q1</strong>: Can the chatbot handle multilingual conversations?</p>
<p><strong>Answer</strong>: Yes, the chatbot supports multiple languages and can be trained to understand and respond in different languages.</p>
<p><strong>Q2</strong>: Is it possible to customize the chatbot’s responses based on specific user preferences?</p>
<p><strong>Answer</strong>: Absolutely, the chatbot’s responses can be customized through configuration settings to tailor responses according to user preferences.</p>
